headline: Is It Time To Reassess ResMed (RMD) After Recent Sleep Care Tailwinds?
summary: If you are wondering whether ResMed's current share price still offers value, this article walks through what the numbers are actually saying about the stock today. ResMed recently closed at US$260.70, with reported returns of 3.9% over 7 days, 5.4% over 30 days, 6.5% year to date, 10.9% over 1 year, 16.9% over 3 years, and 25.3% over 5 years. This gives useful context before looking at valuation. Recent headlines around ResMed have focused on ongoing interest in sleep and respiratory care...
